[
  {
    "startTime": 0.266,
    "endTime": 1.534,
    "text": "And now I thought I'd share some of my favorite"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1.534,
    "endTime": 2.702,
    "text": "\"How I Got Dumped\" stories from you guys."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 2.702,
    "endTime": 6.390000000000001,
    "text": "Here we go. This first one's from @kyleosmon."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.39,
    "endTime": 7.507,
    "text": "He said..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.0,
    "endTime": 9.0,
    "text": "A girl in middle school cancelled our movie date over voicemail."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.0,
    "endTime": 14.0,
    "text": "My parents heard the message before I did and woke me up to tell me. So essentially my parents broke up with me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.714,
    "endTime": 17.751,
    "text": "It's like, \"What's going on?\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.751,
    "endTime": 19.185000000000002,
    "text": "Wake up!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.185,
    "endTime": 23.229999999999997,
    "text": "This ones from @ItsNotTheFall."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.23,
    "endTime": 25.225,
    "text": "\"It's not the fall\"?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.225,
    "endTime": 26.693,
    "text": "Is that a famous thing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.693,
    "endTime": 29.195,
    "text": "It's not, it's not the fall."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.195,
    "endTime": 30.397,
    "text": "Talking about seasons?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.598,
    "endTime": 34.234,
    "text": "It's not the fall that hurts..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.234,
    "endTime": 36.503,
    "text": "The coffee? The bunk?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.503,
    "endTime": 37.904,
    "text": "The rehab?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.105,
    "endTime": 40.739,
    "text": "I'm thinking skiing. I'm thinking skiing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.74,
    "endTime": 44.344,
    "text": "Oh, I was thinking falling from grace, yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.78,
    "endTime": 46.212,
    "text": "Oh, you were thinking fall from grace."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.212,
    "endTime": 47.480000000000004,
    "text": "Yeah, like, you know, you hit rock bottom,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.48,
    "endTime": 49.748,
    "text": "you have to go to rehab. \t\tSomething like that, whatever."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.617,
    "endTime": 52.385,
    "text": "-Everything okay, man?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.119,
    "endTime": 55.188,
    "text": "I'm sleeping on my couch in the office."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.188,
    "endTime": 57.57,
    "text": "We'll talk about this later. We shouldn't say this --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.57,
    "endTime": 59.225,
    "text": "shouldn't do it on national television."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.225,
    "endTime": 61.928000000000004,
    "text": "This is from @ItsNotTheFall."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.928,
    "endTime": 64.831,
    "text": "She says.."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.0,
    "endTime": 69.0,
    "text": "I was waiting for my boyfriend at a restaurant when the waiter came and removed the other chair and place setting."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.0,
    "endTime": 72.0,
    "text": "He said they'd received a phone call and I no longer needed the other setting."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.408,
    "endTime": 77.644,
    "text": "-Oh, come on! -It's not the fall."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.644,
    "endTime": 79.44600000000001,
    "text": "-Yeah, not the fall. -Holy moly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.446,
    "endTime": 82.582,
    "text": "If that ever happened... Wow, wow, wow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.582,
    "endTime": 85.184,
    "text": "This one's from @notglue."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.119,
    "endTime": 89.556,
    "text": "-Not the fall and not glue."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.556,
    "endTime": 93.46,
    "text": "-Not glue. -That's not glue, dude."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.433,
    "endTime": 102.10000000000001,
    "text": "Andrew Karn."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.903,
    "endTime": 106.30600000000001,
    "text": "He says..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.0,
    "endTime": 108.0,
    "text": "My girlfriend had a dream she was getting mugged and I wasn't helping her."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.0,
    "endTime": 111.0,
    "text": "She woke up and broke up with me for not defending her...in her dream."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.12,
    "endTime": 116.21600000000001,
    "text": "-\"I had nothing to do --\" -There's other stuff going on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.318,
    "endTime": 121.187,
    "text": "-This one's from @matadorchick."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.187,
    "endTime": 122.856,
    "text": "-Ooh. Nice. No bull."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.856,
    "endTime": 125.725,
    "text": "-She likes matadors. -Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.725,
    "endTime": 128.46,
    "text": "-She says..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.0,
    "endTime": 131.0,
    "text": "After a fight, my boyfriend threw up his hands and said, \"Well folks, that's the ball game.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.998,
    "endTime": 134.233,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.234,
    "endTime": 134.767,
    "text": "That's it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.767,
    "endTime": 136.2,
    "text": "Well, folks, that's the ball game."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.2,
    "endTime": 138.171,
    "text": "Lates."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.171,
    "endTime": 140.874,
    "text": "This one's from @Ash10G."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.874,
    "endTime": 142.841,
    "text": "She says..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.0,
    "endTime": 145.0,
    "text": "My boyfriend told me he \"doesn't have the work ethic\" to keep me happy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.587,
    "endTime": 157.89,
    "text": "-This last one's from @kalsimanmeet."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.9,
    "endTime": 159.392,
    "text": "He says..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.0,
    "endTime": 161.0,
    "text": "My girlfriend asked me how to block someone on WhatsApp."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.0,
    "endTime": 165.0,
    "text": "After I sent the last piece of the instructions, I noticed I wasn't able to send her messages anymore."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.832,
    "endTime": 166.465,
    "text": "There you have it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.466,
    "endTime": 167.901,
